values: The beret looks ridiculous, but at least it's less conspicuous than the ears. Makes it difficult to hear, though, but that can't be helped. He needs to remember to add "petting small animals" to his "things to avoid doing in the Nexus" list. At least these things aren't supposed to last very long.

Scribbled on the back of a receipt for two packs of Seven Stars and box of cheese flavor CalorieMate: Things to look up: - "Nexus" - "AVF" Things to buy at the store: - Tuna - Ice cream - Raisins (brown and gold)
